spirent.methodology.VerifyDbQueryCommand.SqlQuery: SELECT StreamBlockName AS Service, '192.85.1.3' AS Source, '192.85.1.3' AS Destination, 100 AS 'S-Vlan', 100 AS 'C-Vlan', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', Lp.Load || CASE Lp.LoadUnit WHEN 'PERCENT_LINE_RATE' THEN '%' WHEN 'BITS_PER_SECOND' THEN 'bps' WHEN 'KILOBITS_PER_SECOND' THEN 'Kbps' WHEN 'MEGABITS_PER_SECOND' THEN 'Mbps' WHEN 'FRAMES_PER_SECOND' THEN 'Fps' ELSE '' END AS 'CIR', TxRes.FrameCount-RxRes.FrameCount AS 'FL Count', ROUND(CAST(TxRes.FrameCount-RxRes.FrameCount AS FLOAT)/TxRes.FrameCount,3) AS 'FLR', ROUND(MinLatency*1e3,3) AS 'Min FTD (ms)', ROUND(AvgLatency*1e3,3) AS 'Mean FTD (ms)', ROUND(MaxLatency*1e3,3) AS 'Max FTD (ms)', ROUND(MinJitter*1e3,3) AS 'Min FDV (ms)', ROUND(AvgJitter*1e3,3) AS 'Mean FDV (ms)', ROUND(MaxJitter*1e3,3) AS 'Max FDV (ms)', OutSeqFrameCount AS 'Out of Sequence Frame Count', LateFrameCount AS 'Late Frame Count' FROM TxEotStreamResults AS TxRes INNER JOIN RxEotStreamResults AS RxRes ON TxRes.ParentStreamBlock == RxRes.ParentStreamBlock INNER JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON TxRes.ParentStreamBlock IN (5460)INNER JOIN StreamBlockLoadProfile As Lp ON Sb.Handle||','||Lp.Handle = (SELECT SourceHnd||','||TargetHnd FROM RelationTable WHERE Type='AffiliationStreamBlockLoadProfile') WHERE Sb.Handle IN (5460)
spirent.methodology.VerifyDbQueryCommand.Name: Results: Verify CBS Summary Results

spirent.methodology.VerifyMultipleDbQuer.SqlQueryList: {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', AvgJitter AS 'RFC 4689 Avg Jitter (us)', '50.0' AS 'Expected RFC 4689 Avg Jitter (us)' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE AvgJitter > 50.0} {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', MaxJitter AS 'Max Jitter (us)', '200.0' AS 'Expected Max Jitter (us)' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE MaxJitter > 200.0} {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', AvgLatency AS 'Avg Latency (us)', '700.0' AS 'Expected Avg Latency (us)' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE AvgLatency > 700.0} {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', MaxLatency AS 'Max Latency (us)', '1000.0' AS 'Expected Max Latency (us)' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE MaxLatency > 1000.0} {Select StreamBlockName AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', TxRes.FrameCount - RxRes.FrameCount As 'Packet Loss', '0' AS 'Expected Frame Loss' From RxEotStreamResults As RxRes JOIN TxEotStreamResults As TxRes JOIN Streamblock As Sb ON RxRes.ParentStreamBlock = TxRes.ParentStreamblock AND TxRes.ParentStreamblock = Sb.Handle WHERE TxRes.FrameCount - RxRes.FrameCount > 0} {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', OutSeqFrameCount As 'Out of Order Packet Count', '0' AS 'Expected Max Out of Order Packet Count' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE OutSeqFrameCount > 0} {SELECT Name AS 'Streamblock', Sb.FixedFrameLength AS 'Frame Size (bytes)', LateFrameCount As 'Late Packet Count', '0' AS 'Expected Max Late Packet Count' FROM RxEotStreamResults As RxStr JOIN StreamBlock AS Sb ON RxStr.ParentStreamBlock == Sb.Handle WHERE LateFrameCount > 0}
